Russia Offers Japan to Help With Nuclear Accident, RIA Reports

-- B y   H e n r y   M e y e r
-- 
2011-03-13T13:44:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-13/russia-offers-japan-to-help-with-nuclear-accident-ria-reports.html
Russia has offered  Japan  to help
with the accident at the Fukushima nuclear power plant, RIA
Novosti reported, citing Alexander Lokshin, deputy head of
Rosatom Corp., the state-run nuclear power company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Henry Meyer in Moscow at 
